import csv
import pandas as pd

with open("MQD_1465_final.csv", encoding='utf-8') as f:
    reader = csv.reader(f, delimiter=',', quotechar='"', skipinitialspace=True)
    data = list(reader)

# Criar DataFrame manualmente
header, *rows = data
df = pd.DataFrame(rows, columns=header)
